register.description: IP Revision identifier (X.Y.R) Used by software to track features, bugs, and compatibility

bitfield.description: IP Revision

register.description: This register defines the widths of the TX and RX buses on the C2C interface.

bitfield.description: 0000: Bus width is set to 8 bits (default mode).Other values are reserved, and should not be used. .

bitenum.description: Bus width is set to 10 bits (possible only if TX = 8).
Bus width is set to 16 bits.

bitfield.description: 0000: Bus width is set to 8 bits.Other values are reserved, and shall not be used. .

bitenum.description: Bus width is set to 10 bits (possible only if RX = 8).
Bus width is set to 16 bits (default mode).

register.description: This register sets the C2C L3 in mirror mode. See debug section.

bitfield.description: Mirror mode.
